============
Graph Theory
============


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/graphtheory.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/graphtheory

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/somacdivad/graphtheory.svg
        :target: https://travis-ci.org/somacdivad/graphtheory

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/graphtheory/badge/?version=latest
        :target: https://graphtheory.readthedocs.io/en/latest/?badge=latest
        :alt: Documentation Status




A lightweight graph library for Python.


* Free software: MIT license
* Documentation: https://graphtheory.readthedocs.io.


Philisophy
----------

- Use only the standard library.
- Use no more memory than is necessary.
- Package API should be as friendly as possible *to the trained graph theorist*.
- Source should be as readable as possible *to the trained graph theorist*.


Credits
-------

This package was created with Cookiecutter_ and the `audreyr/cookiecutter-pypackage`_ project template.

.. _Cookiecutter: https://github.com/audreyr/cookiecutter
